title: #461 - Fahim Anwar
description:
Fahim Anwar, a standup comedian and actor seen in "Whiskey Tango Foxtrot,"  joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.
  
Fahim has a new special, "There's No Business Like Show Business," which premiers March 9th, 2017 on Seeso.
